				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The frequency written to the 11 bit timer counts down before the duty cycle counter is adjusted... so in this sense there's actually two counters.
<br />
<br />- Frequency counter counts down every cycle
<br />- When frequency counter reaches 0, it's reloaded and the <em>duty cycle</em> counter is incremented (wrapping at 7-&gt;0).
<br />- Output is based on the duty cycle counter's position.  The value in the frequency counter is irrelevent.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

